<B>__{basketball court}
<A>__{doctor spivey is at half court, basketball in hand as the players take up their positions: washington faces mcmurphy for the jump at center. harding and billy are playing guard with warren and miller on them. martini and scanlon are in the forward position, with the two white aides covering them. the other acutes sit on the bench as substitutes.}
